title: History Made! First Win for all-new Ford GT
description: Race footage from the all-new Ford GT's first win at Laguna Seca (Salinas, Calif.). Features checkered flag, victory lane celebration and interviews with drivers Richard Westbrook and Ryan Briscoe.
